List of operations in the KEGG REST API

Source: R/keggrest.R
kegg_operations.Rd

List of operations in the KEGG REST API

Usage

kegg_operations()

Value

A character vector of KEGG operations.

Examples

kegg_operations()
#> [1] "info" "list" "find" "get"  "conv" "link" "ddi"
